Package org.eclipse.collections.impl.map.mutable.primitive

Class SynchronizedLongShortMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.collections.impl.map.mutable.primitive.SynchronizedLongShortMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, LongShortMap, MutableLongShortMap, MutableShortValuesMap, ShortValuesMap, PrimitiveIterable, ShortIterable
    public class SynchronizedLongShortMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements MutableLongShortMap, java.io.Serializable
    A synchronized view of a MutableLongShortMap. It is imperative that the user manually synchronize on the collection when iterating over it using the MutableShortIterator as per Collections.synchronizedCollection(Collection).

    This file was automatically generated from template file synchronizedPrimitivePrimitiveMap.stg.

    Since:
    3.1.
    See Also:
    MutableLongShortMap.asSynchronized(), MutableMap.asSynchronized(), Serialized Form
